---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/blogHome.css';
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "Lola-Rose's Blog";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<h1>{pageTitle}<i>&nbsp;~</i></h1>
        <p>Welcome! I created this blog as a way of documenting my progress as the years go on. I will be posting a few snippets of things I have made, learned and more! I hope you enjoy reading it as much as I will enjoy making it :)</p>
        <ul>
            <li class="post"><a href="/posts/post-1">Post 1</a></li>
        </ul>
		<Footer />
		<script>
			import "../scripts/menu.js";
		</script>
    </body>
</html>
